The Updates of COVID-19 in Republic of Korea
As of 28 February, 2020

○ Compared to yesterday morning (09:00, 27 February, 2020), 427 additional cases are confirmed, which brings the total number of confirmed cases to 2,022 with 1,983 cases in isolation. 44,167 turned out to be negative and 24,751 are currently being tested.





